short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a stylesheet for MSU's MyInfo

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The purpose of the MyInfo+ extension is to improve the look and functionality of Montana State University's MyInfo website. It provides a togglable stylesheet, and fixes the logout redirect.
